<%# Testimonials with metrics %>
<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-white" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl text-center mb-16" data-reveal-item>
      What cooperative leaders<span class="text-[#5b8c5a]"> are saying</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-8 bg-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="landing-metric">45 min → seconds</span>
          </div>
          <span class="landing-pullquote-mark">"</span>
          <p class="landing-pullquote-text pl-6">Our tellers had been handwriting passbooks for decades. They were the most skeptical when we started. By day two, they were showing me how end-of-day used to take 45 minutes — now it's done before the last member leaves.</p>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#e7e5e4]">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">General Manager</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">Luzon Cooperative</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-[#5b8c5a] p-8 bg-[#f0f7ef]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="landing-metric">3 binders → 1 screen</span>
          </div>
          <span class="landing-pullquote-mark">"</span>
          <p class="landing-pullquote-text pl-6">Our loan officer kept everything in ring binders — not because she was disorganised, but because the systems she had didn't talk to each other. When she saw a member's complete profile appear on one screen, she said it felt like getting an assistant.</p>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#b8d4b5]">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Operations Manager</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">Visayas Cooperative</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-8 bg-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="landing-metric">3 yrs → 1 weekend</span>
          </div>
          <span class="landing-pullquote-mark">"</span>
          <p class="landing-pullquote-text pl-6">I spent three years trying to get board approval. Every vendor wanted a long commitment and a price tag that scared everyone. Sirib was running alongside our old setup in a weekend. The board saw the difference — and our team never felt forced.</p>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#e7e5e4]">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Treasurer</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">Mindanao Cooperative</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

