        <div data-accordion-target="content" hidden class="px-6 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">
          Absolutely. Sirib imports your existing member IDs, account numbers, and loan reference numbers. Members see no change — their account is the same, their passbook prints the same way.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

